    <entry>
      <title>stl-map,set的自定义排序</title>
      <link href="/2022/11/30/stl-map-set%E7%9A%84%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F/"/>
      <url>/2022/11/30/stl-map-set%E7%9A%84%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="set"><a href="#set" class="headerlink" title="set"></a>set</h1><p>使用二叉树实现的容器，元素插入自动排序。</p><h2 id="声明"><a href="#声明" class="headerlink" title="声明"></a>声明</h2><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">set&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 默认小根堆，如果需要降序：</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">mycmp</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="function"><span class="type">bool</span> <span class="title">operator</span><span class="params">()</span> <span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> a, <span class="type">int</span> b)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> a &gt; b;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">set&lt;<span class="type">int</span>, mycmp&gt; s;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="函数"><a href="#函数" class="headerlink" title="函数"></a>函数</h2><p><strong>find()</strong></p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">s.<span class="built_in">find</span>(x) </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>x为查找的元素，返回指向元素k的迭代器，不存在这个元素，返回s.end()，用于判断元素中有没有这个元素，划重点，复杂度o(lgN)</p><p><strong>insert()</strong></p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">s.<span class="built_in">insert</span>(x)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>插入元素x</p><p><strong>erase()</strong></p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">s.<span class="built_in">erase</span>(x)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>删除元素x</p><h2 id="multiset与set的区别和用法"><a href="#multiset与set的区别和用法" class="headerlink" title="multiset与set的区别和用法"></a>multiset与set的区别和用法</h2><p>multiset中可存储重复元素，不满足唯一性。</p><p>multiset 调用erase()会删除所有等于x的元素，如果只想删除一个：</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>((it = s.<span class="built_in">find</span>(a)) != s.<span class="built_in">end</span>())</span><br><span class="line">    s.<span class="built_in">erase</span>(it);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>count()在multiset中就显得有大作用了，返回元素的个数。</p><p><strong>set实现结构体排序</strong></p><p>结构体里面重载&lt;即可：</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title class_">tnode</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> x, id;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">bool</span> <span class="keyword">operator</span> &lt; (<span class="type">const</span> tnode&amp; a) <span class="type">const</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> x == a.x ? id &lt; a.id : x &gt; a.x;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">set&lt;tnode&gt; st;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="map"><a href="#map" class="headerlink" title="map"></a>map</h1><h2 id="按照key排序"><a href="#按照key排序" class="headerlink" title="按照key排序"></a>按照key排序</h2><p>跟set基本一致，如果写仿函数的话：</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">map&lt;string, <span class="type">int</span>, mycmp&gt; mp;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="按照value排序"><a href="#按照value排序" class="headerlink" title="按照value排序"></a>按照value排序</h2><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">map&lt;string,<span class="type">int</span>&gt; mp;</span><br><span class="line">vector&lt;pair&lt;string,<span class="type">int</span>&gt;&gt; <span class="built_in">v</span>(mp.<span class="built_in">begin</span>(),mp.<span class="built_in">end</span>()); <span class="comment">//将map中的元素拷贝到vector中</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">sort</span>(v.<span class="built_in">begin</span>(), v.<span class="built_in">end</span>(), mycmp); <span class="comment">//实现value的排序</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
